organic.title: Hospice Care - Kaiser Permanente
organic.snippet: Discusses hospice care, which includes medical, emotional, and spiritual care for people who are in the last stages of a serious illness.

organic.title: Kaiser Permanente Northern California Hospice
organic.snippet: Kaiser Permanente Hospice offers care and comfort in your home. We provide pain and symptom control, as well as emotional and spiritual support.

organic.title: Hospice - Care at Home - Kaiser Permanente
organic.snippet: Hospice is care provided to a person who has been diagnosed with a terminal illness. Hospice care provides you with physical, emotional and spiritual comfort.

organic.title: Kaiser Permanente Hospice Services
organic.snippet: Our hospice care team comes to your home, where we help support the family, friends, and hired caregivers responsible for your day-to-day care.

organic.title: Medicare Hospice Benefit - Kaiser Permanente
organic.snippet: The Medicare hospice benefit covers care related to a terminal illness. Medicare is a health insurance program for people 65 years of age and older.
